' Hide technical details for clarity
hide circle
skinparam linetype ortho

entity \"owners\" as owners {
 *owner_id : number
 --
 owner_name : varchar(100)
 email : varchar(100)
 phone : varchar(20)
}

entity \"tenants\" as tenants {
 *tenant_id : number
 --
 tenant_name : varchar(100)
 email : varchar(100)
 phone : varchar(20)
}

entity \"flats\" as flats {
 *flat_id : number
 --
 address : varchar(255)
 area : number(5,2)
 rooms : number(2)
 owner_id : number
}

entity \"contracts\" as contracts {
 *contract_id : number
 --
 flat_id : number
 tenant_id : number
 start_date : date
 end_date : date
 rent_amount : number(7,2)
}

entity \"payments\" as payments {
 *payment_id : number
 --
 contract_id : number
 payment_date : date
 amount : number(7,2)
 status : char(10)
}

entity \"service_companies\" as service_companies {
 *company_id : number
 --
 company_name : varchar(100)
 email : varchar(100)
 phone : varchar(20)
}

entity \"employees\" as employees {
 *employee_id : number
 --
 employee_name : varchar(100)
 role : varchar(50)
 email : varchar(100)
}

entity \"requests\" as requests {
 *request_id : number
 --
 flat_id : number
 tenant_id : number
 description : varchar(500)
 request_date : date
 status : char(15)
}

entity \"service_actions\" as service_actions {
 *action_id : number
 --
 request_id : number
 employee_id : number
 company_id : number
 action_date : date
 note : varchar(500)
}

' Relationships
owners ||--o{ flats : owns
flats ||--o{ contracts : has
tenants ||--o{ contracts : signs
contracts ||--o{ payments : triggers
flats ||--o{ requests : gets
tenants ||--o{ requests : creates
requests ||--o{ service_actions : results in
employees ||--o{ service_actions : handles
service_companies ||--o{ service_actions : provides

@enduml
